metadata.title: Cessna 182 Skylane
aws::graph::propositions: # Cessna 182 Skylane Model History
Cessna 182 Skylane was certified on 7 December 1956.
1713 total Cessna 182 Skylane units were built in the initial production run.
911 Cessna 182 Skylane units were built in 1957.
802 Cessna 182 Skylane units were built in 1958.
Cessna 182B was the 1959 model year of the Cessna 182 Skylane.
Cessna 182B featured a more streamlined cowling with cowl flaps.
Cessna 182B featured a new instrument panel cover.
Cessna 182B featured improved ventilation.
Cessna 182B was certified on 22 August 1958.
802 Cessna 182B units were built.
Cessna 182C was the 1960 model year of the Cessna 182 Skylane.
Cessna 182C featured a redesigned swept vertical tail.
Cessna 182C featured smaller wing root fillets.
Cessna 182C cabin was redesigned with more headroom.
Cessna 182C featured molded plastic control wheels.
Cessna 182C featured a third cabin window.
Cessna 182C was certified on 8 July 1959.
650 Cessna 182C units were built.
Four largely identical L-19L models were built for the Canadian Army.
Cessna 182D was the 1961 model year of the Cessna 182 Skylane.
Cessna 182D featured a key start switch.
Cessna 182D featured cam-lock cowling fasteners.
Cessna 182D featured decreased landing gear height.
Cessna 182D was certified on 14 June 1960.
591 Cessna 182D units were built.

text:
Certified on 7 December 1956.  1713 total built; 911 (1957) and 802 (1958).
182B
1959 model year with a more streamlined cowling with cowl flaps, a new instrument panel cover, and improved ventilation.  Certified on 22 August 1958.  802 built.
182C
1960 model year with a redesigned swept vertical tail and smaller wing root fillets.  The cabin was also redesigned with more headroom, molded plastic control wheels, and a third cabin window.  Certified on 8 July 1959.  650 built, plus four largely identical L-19L models for the Canadian Army.
182D
1961 model year with a key start switch, cam-lock cowling fasteners, and decreased landing gear height.  Certified on 14 June 1960.  591 built.
